    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exertion</strong> 是一款类 Rogue 横版动作游戏，背景设定在 AI 控制的战争机器主宰战场的反乌托邦未来。作为一名高科技战斗机器人，你必须在无尽的敌方无人机浪潮中奋力战斗，每个敌人都拥有致命的能力。适应战局，不断升级，并精进你的战斗技巧，以在逐渐升级的挑战中生存下去。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>技能</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人以解锁强力升级，提升你的战斗技能。尝试不同的组合，打造符合你个人风格的战斗方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/fd2bca18522b87192c58231e03ce0a12.poster.avif?t=1771422018\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/fd2bca18522b87192c58231e03ce0a12.webm?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/fd2bca18522b87192c58231e03ce0a12.mp4?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>卡牌选择</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗结束后，你可以选择不同的升级卡牌。你会专注于纯粹的火力、极限机动，还是战术防御？选择权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/e67e5644aeddb5e21c7a73419e7e2050.poster.avif?t=1771422018\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/e67e5644aeddb5e21c7a73419e7e2050.webm?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/e67e5644aeddb5e21c7a73419e7e2050.mp4?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>BOSS 战</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接与巨大战争机器的史诗级对决。每个 Boss 都有独特的攻击模式，将考验你的反应能力和适应能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/b9347a97fba6be602fb78e56e2142afe.poster.avif?t=1771422018\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/b9347a97fba6be602fb78e56e2142afe.webm?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/b9347a97fba6be602fb78e56e2142afe.mp4?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>探索地图</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满敌人的走廊中奋战，解锁新的区域。警惕隐藏的威胁，同时寻找战略要点，扭转战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/2ace8ed4618e35513ca11309c81cf380.poster.avif?t=1771422018\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/2ace8ed4618e35513ca11309c81cf380.webm?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/2ace8ed4618e35513ca11309c81cf380.mp4?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>选择武器</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备你的武器，解锁独特的战斗优势，并根据战斗情况调整战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/dc379efba9f209016f58f7643c597ac4.poster.avif?t=1771422018\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/dc379efba9f209016f58f7643c597ac4.webm?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164600/extras/dc379efba9f209016f58f7643c597ac4.mp4?t=1771422018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验试玩版，立即投入战斗！解锁强大的新武器，完成富有挑战性的任务，并不断强化你的角色，每次尝试都能更进一步。你的反馈将塑造 <strong>Exertion</strong> 的未来！</p>",
